- cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) is relevant as the CONGEST model is a network-based model for distributed computation. 
- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) could be relevant as subgraph detection is a common problem in network analysis. 
- cs.AL (Computational Complexity) is less likely but still possible as the paper discusses the complexity of the algorithms and their optimality.
